{"tid":1912514,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[迷思] 到底真雙普選放唔放棄","createTime":"2020-03-06T06:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T10:03:46.000Z","uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5758034abdaffaf193672c3ff3dcb42acbda659a","tid":1912514,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"近呢幾個月 有2個風向<br />\n1. 叫人去登記做功能組別選民 去選功能界別議員 <br />\n2. 屌9人仲喺小圈子入面玩 唔可以選功能組別<br />\n<br />\n理想: 本身功能組別個制度根本就 <span style=\"color: gold;\">不公義</span> 點撚解要喺入面玩? 仲跟制度玩根本就推翻唔到政權<br />\n現實: 問心 泛民可以全部人齊心廢除功能界別咩? 如果參與小圈子功能界別 長遠會損害抗爭理據<br />\n<br />\n唔係想做冷氣軍師 只係想大家一齊討論 攞個共識唔好內鬥唔好互屌<br />\n不如大家投下票睇下初步對呢件事嘅立場?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 應該放棄 真雙普選只系口號（同阿彌佗佛一樣）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔應該放棄 爭雙普選係為自己為後代"},{"pid":"165c920c4f04914b36e41680fe1b223c8494f1b1","tid":1912514,"uid":79680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"獨立"},{"pid":"24d72c4863f702720574fa8a29ed51ffe2c486f5","tid":1912514,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"165c920c4f04914b36e41680fe1b223c8494f1b1","tid":1912514,"uid":79680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"獨立 同 放唔放棄真雙普選 冇牴觸"},{"pid":"ed595728e309649521780c7c3268fb7ab4e8ced6","tid":1912514,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NnMZ3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NnMZ3e.jpg&h=bcff8976&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cd39161133e3afd1ed3cfd55da3b2133e83b5a3","tid":1912514,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}